Fig. 2 A
): Neotype ♀ (designated here) in MZUC, nº 1907 , two labels, one labelled “ Angola ” (white label printed), other labelled “M.Z.U.C., registo nº 1907 ” (blue label, printed and handwritten), design. A. Serrano (red printed).

